Inside the [bluetooth]# prompt:

    power on
    agent on
    default-agent
    scan on (Turn on your headphones pairing mode now)
    Wait for your device to appear, then note the MAC address (e.g., XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX).
    pair XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX
    trust XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX (To allow auto-connect later)
    connect XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX
    quit

devices Trusted - list zaufanych urzadzen
